{"tid":1382771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"同門防彈少年團不是第一次！ GFRIEND二成員「過去也是BigHit練習生」","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T04:46:29.000Z","uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6682bbbd02e100c4fb7bf03914586a1494322a3b","tid":1382771,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"世界知名韓團防彈少年團（BTS）所屬公司BigHit娛樂29日宣布驚人消息，併購了在KPOP界擁有一席地位的女團GFRIEND所屬公司SOURCE MUSIC。然而對於GFRIEND部分成員來說，這次的併購其實是「再次回到BigHit」，因為Eunha和SinB過去也曾是該公司的練習生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4235/d4235211.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4235%2Fd4235211.jpg&h=dc2cd650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團所屬的BigHit娛樂，宣布併購GFRIEND所屬公司SOURCE MUSIC。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n外界對BigHit娛樂的印象是該公司不僅只推出男團，旗下練習生也通通是男生，一度被笑稱是「和尚學校」。但事實上，BigHit娛樂過去也曾推出過女團「GLAM」，當初由朴智妍、金珍熙、金多喜、李微笑共四人組成，不過成員金多喜在2014年爆發小模李智妍涉嫌拍私密影片勒索李秉憲，最終遭南韓警方逮捕並起訴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4269/d4269690.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4269%2Fd4269690.jpg&h=41ee38cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BigHit娛樂過去推出過女團「GLAM」。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n金多喜因此欠下經紀公司約3億韓元，「GLAM」也於2015年宣布解散，此後BigHit娛樂也與當時旗下所有女練習生解約，專注培訓男練習生和男歌手。當時解約的女練習生中，就包括GFRIEND成員Eunha和SinB，以及Nine Muses成員笑珍、Cherry Bullet成員海允、彩麟等人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4269/d4269689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4269%2Fd4269689.jpg&h=49da37a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND成員Eunha和SinB，以前也是BigHit娛樂的練習生。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n不過雖然Eunha和SinB之後到了SOURCE MUSIC，但該公司代表蘇成鎮，其實和BigHit娛樂代表房時爀是多年好友，兩間公司當時都還只是「中小型企劃社」，連訓練練習生的老師們都共用。如今BigHit娛樂收購SOURCE MUSIC，登上NAVER熱搜，不只粉絲討論就連一般網友也對此話題展現高度興趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4268/d4268211.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4268%2Fd4268211.jpg&h=795f2eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BigHit娛樂宣布併購GFRIEND所屬公司SOURCE MUSIC，在業界投下震撼彈。（圖／翻攝自推特）"},{"pid":"c6084024bb7e3c0a8b616960337cb17c6088bfc7","tid":1382771,"uid":76098,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"好怕呢次合併會增加銀河大髀口水漬"},{"pid":"1d4bd21e6ddae733f6ef390e37949ddb575ef1e5","tid":1382771,"uid":193951,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"咪開啦 陣間又有狗入黎話黐佢地金糠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fc581cc6711fa04f579fade9d8eee064e2c4e7","tid":1382771,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6084024bb7e3c0a8b616960337cb17c6088bfc7","tid":1382771,"uid":76098,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"好怕呢次合併會增加銀河大髀口水漬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"你想你大髀撻口水漬都增加？"},{"pid":"635fb959e1f9b2f0410faff3c2b02fc3a9ce906e","tid":1382771,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45fc581cc6711fa04f579fade9d8eee064e2c4e7","tid":1382771,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6084024bb7e3c0a8b616960337cb17c6088bfc7","tid":1382771,"uid":76098,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"好怕呢次合併會增加銀河大髀口水漬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"你想你大髀撻口水漬都增加？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"你家陣係咪威脅我"},{"pid":"4b6d105efd9d89c5e93d80c886e017efc14b1a7d","tid":1382771,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d4bd21e6ddae733f6ef390e37949ddb575ef1e5","tid":1382771,"uid":193951,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"咪開啦 陣間又有狗入黎話黐佢地金糠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"個D傻鳩黎"},{"pid":"32eb330d9cb160c0b1e6b3a48255a9090dff511a","tid":1382771,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":12,"sco